      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAIL AWAY SAM (1) charged out of the boxes with a fast early split and led throughout to score when a 4 length winner (22.88) over 400m at this track. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Form reads well for this. MADE IN LONDON (2) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at Taree Super Track in a handy 17.52 beating Ice On Fire. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Leading chance again. KALANI SEA (5) boasts a strong record this journey here with six wins and five minors from 16 tries. Missed the frame latest (25.31) when sixth over 431m at Gunnedah in a Grade 5. Looks well placed here and among the chances. STOP IT ZIPPER (7) is a last-start placegetter as favourite - should be thereabouts.",
